data.description: Here's your STUNNING COLONIAL CONTEMPORARY in Aboite's desirable Haverhill! * 2350SF 4BR 2.5BA * Well Maintained Home on the Tranquil Grounds of the Wooded Green! * Enjoy MULTIPLE LIVING SPACES! – Living Room off Foyer & A Hearth Family Room blending into Casual Dining & Kitchen while opening onto a large Wooded Back Yard with Cobblestone Patio & Sun Lounge! * Your COOK'S KITCHEN features Bountiful Counterspace, Solid Surface Floor & adjoining Casual & Formal Dining Areas * TWO MASTER SUITES & 2 other comfortably sized bedrooms upstairs * Large Lot with Lush Landscaping, Fenced Back Yard, Dining Patio, Campfire Ring & Vast Woods for exploration! * 2 Car Oversized Garage * SWAC Schools! * Close to YMCA, Homestead HS, Lutheran, I-69 & Great Neighbors!
